      "title": "Shortage of 120 medicines",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "However, the shortage of 14 life-saving drugs has been addressed, said Director of Medical Technology Services, Dr. Anwar Hamdani.",
        "He also informed that steps are being taken to overcome the shortage of equipment such as contact lenses and hearing aids and surgical equipments these days. (R)"
